exthheader.author: Jim Butcher
exthheader.description: SUMMARY: In the realm of Alera, where people bond with the furies--elementals of earth, air, fire, water, wood, and metal--fifteen-year-old Tavi struggles with his lack of furycrafting. But when his homeland erupts in chaos--when rebels war with loyalists and furies clash with furies-- Tavi's simple courage will turn the tides of war.
exthheader.subject: Unabridged Audio - Fiction
